{"tid":1504067,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家不如搞搞佢","createTime":"2019-08-25T07:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T07:42:45.000Z","uid":228729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7843592129acecd3c085d23cc315c4a27812bc4b","tid":1504067,"uid":228729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:42:45.000Z","msg":"名可以亂填<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊搞搞佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n***********************************************<br />\n<br />\n聯署要求所有參加罷課的學生即時退學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不論大學或中學教育都是受納稅人資助其學位的。而作為學生的本份就是學習。如果他們覺得有其他事情比學習與上課更重要，那請他們即時退學去做那些他們覺得更重要的事情。騰出來的學位就可以給那些真正希望學習/讀書的人。避免浪費寶貴的社會資源。所有聯署人現在一致要求特首及各院校校長開除這批參加罷課學生的學籍。請在下面空格填上聯署人稱呼：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/mRfS9JgDujVVVsCYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FmRfS9JgDujVVVsCYA&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DkWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=22e63b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/mRfS9JgDujVVVsCYA</a><br />\n<br />\n*請廣傳*"}]}